	doesn't get ignored.

Mon May 11 22:24:40 1992  David J. MacKenzie  (djm@churchy.gnu.ai.mit.edu)

	* updatedb.sh: Allow many vars to be overridden in the environment.

	* locate.c, updatedb.sh: FCODES -> LOCATE_DB.

